  "detailed_description": "Jax is your teleporting cyborg corgi. A Cyborgi, if you will. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nJax wants to play. To him, that means teleporting around the city while you chase after him!  You'll have to use interesting movement mechanics (bunny-hopping, portals, bounce-pads and more!) to bring Jax home before dinner.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nCyborgis still need their exercise - take Jax for a walk with the help of the Steam Workshop!",
